&lt;p&gt;A cloudy week exposes your recovery plan, not just your battery size. If refill windows shrink and daily loads stay steady, even a system that felt fine can become stressful fast. The goal is to protect stability, not chase perfect conditions.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>